(2927,'_site_transient_wp_plugin_dependencies_plugin_data','a:4:{s:14:\"contact-form-7\";a:35:{s:4:\"name\";s:14:\"Contact Form 7\";s:4:\"slug\";s:14:\"contact-form-7\";s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"6.0.2\";s:6:\"author\";s:62:\"<a href=\"https://ideasilo.wordpress.com/\">Takayuki Miyoshi</a>\";s:14:\"author_profile\";s:44:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/takayukister/\";s:12:\"contributors\";a:1:{s:12:\"takayukister\";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:44:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/takayukister/\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:120:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/538487024e649d43dea84ff38d14582d03119e3e7aaaca3b7692443335999133?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:16:\"Takayuki Miyoshi\";}}s:8:\"requires\";s:3:\"6.6\";s:6:\"tested\";s:5:\"6.7.1\";s:12:\"requires_php\";s:3:\"7.4\";s:16:\"requires_plugins\";a:0:{}s:6:\"rating\";i:80;s:7:\"ratings\";a:5:{i:5;i:1430;i:4;i:146;i:3;i:75;i:2;i:68;i:1;i:403;}s:11:\"num_ratings\";i:2122;s:11:\"support_url\";s:52:\"https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/contact-form-7/\";s:15:\"support_threads\";i:181;s:24:\"support_threads_resolved\";i:49;s:15:\"active_installs\";i:10000000;s:12:\"last_updated\";s:21:\"2024-12-22 5:03am GMT\";s:5:\"added\";s:10:\"2007-08-02\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:25:\"https://contactform7.com/\";s:8:\"sections\";a:6:{s:11:\"description\";s:3784:\"<p>Contact Form 7 &#8211; це плагін, розроблений як практичний інструмент для всіх користувачів WordPress, які поділяють філософію вільного програмного забезпечення з відкритим кодом. Він використовує складну модульну архітектуру та оригінальну технологію <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/schema-woven-validation/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Schema-Woven Validation</a>.</p>\n<h4>Документація та підтримка</h4>\n<p>Ви можете знайти <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/docs/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">документи</a>, <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/faq/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">FAQ</a> тощо детальну інформацію про контактну форму 7 на <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">contactform7.com</a>. Якщо ви не можете знайти відповідь на своє запитання в розділі поширених запитань або в будь-якій документації, відвідайте <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/contact-form-7/\" rel=\"ugc\">форум підтримки</a> на WordPress.org. Якщо ви не можете знайти теми, які стосуються вашої конкретної проблеми, опублікуйте для неї нову тему.</p>\n<h4>Contact Form 7 потребує вашої підтримки</h4>\n<p>Важко продовжувати підтримувати цей плагін без підтримки таких користувачів, як ви. Ви можете <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contributing/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">внести свій внесок у проект</a> кількома способами: тестування, кодування, переклад на ваші місцеві мови, допомога іншим користувачам, фінансові пожертви і т.д. Ми однаково вітаємо вас незалежно від того, як ви робите свій внесок.</p>\n<h4>Сповіщення про конфіденційність</h4>\n<p>У стандартній конфігурації, даний плагін сам не буде:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>стежити таємно за користувачами;</li>\n<li>запис будь-яких персональних даних користувача в базу даних;</li>\n<li>надсилання будь-яких даних на зовнішні сервери;</li>\n<li>використовуйте cookies.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Якщо ви активуєте певні функції в цьому плагіні, особисті дані відправника контактної форми, включаючи його IP-адресу, можуть бути відправлені постачальнику послуг. Таким чином, рекомендується підтвердити політику конфіденційності постачальника. Ці функції включають в себе:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>reCAPTCHA (<a href=\"https://policies.google.com/?hl=en\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Google</a>)</li>\n<li>Akismet (<a href=\"https://automattic.com/privacy/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Automattic</a>)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.constantcontact.com/legal/privacy-center\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Постійний контакт</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.brevo.com/legal/privacypolicy/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Brevo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://stripe.com/privacy\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Stripe</a></li>\n</ul>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:662:\"<ol>\n<li>Завантажте папку <code>contact-form-7</code> в директорію <code>/wp-content/plugins/</code>.</li>\n<li>Активуйте плагін через розділ <strong>Плагіни</strong> (<strong>Плагіни &gt; Встановлені плагіни</strong>).</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Ви знайдете меню <strong>Контакти</strong> в розділі адміністратора WordPress.</p>\n<p>Для базового використання ви також можете подивитися на <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">домашню сторінку плагіну</a>.</p>\n\";s:3:\"faq\";s:539:\"<p>У вас є питання або проблеми з Contact Form 7? Використовуйте ці канали підтримки.</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/docs/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Документація</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/faq/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">FAQ</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/contact-form-7/\" rel=\"ugc\">Форум підтримки</a></li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/support/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Підтримка</a></p>\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:1717:\"<p>Для отримання додаткової інформації, дивіться <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/category/releases/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Релізи</a>.</p>\n<h4>6.0.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Видаляє непотрібні оголошення типів з нульових аргументів, щоб уникнути попереджень про застарілість у PHP 8.4.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>6.0.1</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-601/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-601/</a></p>\n<h4>6.0</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-60/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-60/</a></p>\n<h4>5.9.7</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-597/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-597/</a></p>\n<h4>5.9.6</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-596/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-596/</a></p>\n<h4>5.9.5</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-595/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-595/</a></p>\n<h4>5.9.4</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-594/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-594/</a></p>\n<h4>5.9.3</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-593/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-593/</a></p>\n<h4>5.9.2</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-592/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-592/</a></p>\n<h4>5.9</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-59/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://contactform7.com/contact-form-7-59/</a></p>\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:225:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/contact-form-7/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1176454\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/contact-form-7/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1176454\" alt=\"screenshot-1.png\"></a><p>screenshot-1.png</p></li></ol>\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:17788:\"<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Dude what happened</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/alexfreixa/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f9914f8f922eda27cc7167d52b1be04ee58300987cf4c48ed52c2f807eade773?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f9914f8f922eda27cc7167d52b1be04ee58300987cf4c48ed52c2f807eade773?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/alexfreixa/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Alex Freixa <small>(alexfreixa)</small></a> о <span class=\"review-date\">3 Січня, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Why it\'s unusable? This plugin was working so fine. Customize it it\'s a nightmare!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Lack of support, lack of accessibility</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/heggyy/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/84dd541d8963907b9e3fc8406d9e726f54649e658e5ce6d932e769a52e44f92f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/84dd541d8963907b9e3fc8406d9e726f54649e658e5ce6d932e769a52e44f92f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/heggyy/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">heggyy</a> о <span class=\"review-date\">3 Січня, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Overhyped plugin simply because it is free. It is the ultimate barebones of a plugin that people find necessary. There are no features, customizing anything means you are either a) a programmer or b) have to email support (in which case good luck getting help, egos too big). Gets no updates, no features, no accessibility or UX improvements. You\'re better off paying for a plugin than pulling your hair out to get it working as needed.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">quick resposne to questions and support tickets</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/frankyuyong/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e256a8b26bc82e4a27d420c11998d37300d62eeba2f3adcd1adc3daa7398722e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e256a8b26bc82e4a27d420c11998d37300d62eeba2f3adcd1adc3daa7398722e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/frankyuyong/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">frankyuyong</a> о <span class=\"review-date\">11 Грудня, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The team is highly responsive and helpful. They arranged a Google Meet session to assist me with an API and JSON data format issue, thoroughly resolving the problem on my end.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">not working</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/yosragattoufi/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/408c84ff4582155ccee988521d17f0f786153d528d06a500808b644061dd5790?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/408c84ff4582155ccee988521d17f0f786153d528d06a500808b644061dd5790?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/yosragattoufi/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">yosragattoufi</a> о <span class=\"review-date\">4 Грудня, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hello,</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For recaptcha It is not working for us since 2 years. we redesigned the website and it still not working.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When someone submit the form he has an eeror message that the message could not be sent , or it still loading without submission.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I am using the part \"Integration\" on contact form 7</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thanks</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Translation issue and nightmare support.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"2 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"2\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jyria/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f3ffa0afd56f0b53fb075f65fa2657a765d4790567818a3f2c6ac0e2a1126066?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f3ffa0afd56f0b53fb075f65fa2657a765d4790567818a3f2c6ac0e2a1126066?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jyria/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Saskia Teichmann <small>(Jyria)</small></a> о <span class=\"review-date\">26 Листопада, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This free plugin is very useful and has done what it was supposed to do for many years. However, there are a few issues that are very annoying and a total deal breaker, if not a show stopper:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Plugin creator did not comply with WordPress Codex regarding how translations are handled. Thus this plugin will eventually cause problems in a multilingual site.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Forum support by plugin creator is very poor. He replies, yes, but his replies are a joke. He simply doesn\'t care. He doesn\'t read properly nor does he do any testing, even after providing everything he asked for. He is a time stealer.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>My personal resume: I will switch contact forms on all of my clients\' sites. There are better alternatives out there. I am of course willing to pay for support. And this is my suggestion for @takayukister : provide paid support, if you think your time is too valuable, to give a useful reply or provide assistance with your free plugin. Or take that plugin offline or officially state that you won\'t provide support at all and refrain from stealing people\'s time by requesting non sense things and then ignoring them in return.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Horrendous, overcomplicated plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/davepez/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/82710dca0a6524a1bf7c9249795a8f061613e5bb93e57ce8cbae6802f465f528?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/82710dca0a6524a1bf7c9249795a8f061613e5bb93e57ce8cbae6802f465f528?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/davepez/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">davepez</a> о <span class=\"review-date\">24 Листопада, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I\'ve had problems with this plugin for years.  It can appear simple at first but so many times has required a load of custom code to sort the formatting properly and to get it looking right on all devices.  This always takes ages - googling it and finding loads of other people posting that they can\'t do simple things and never any solution.  It should not require so much fannying about!  The support website is useless, too.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Flexible and Reliable Plugin with Great Anti-Spam Features</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mojcak/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a0013f2a939ed42fe21ae2274c85e31b57ef7e3b2ebdd2714265a119bb2ebf3d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a0013f2a939ed42fe21ae2274c85e31b57ef7e3b2ebdd2714265a119bb2ebf3d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mojcak/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">mojcak</a> о <span class=\"review-date\">23 Листопада, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Contact Form 7 is incredibly versatile and adaptable, making it easy to create custom forms for a variety of needs. One of my favorite features is the math-based spam protection, which works very effectively without adding unnecessary complexity. The plugin has been a reliable choice for all my projects. Highly recommended for anyone looking for a robust form solution!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">New Version responsive issue.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sknasib/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ccfeae62d49c8bde406f2837882bac00827771c98b3d0cf5eb6e60bce266c3d4?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ccfeae62d49c8bde406f2837882bac00827771c98b3d0cf5eb6e60bce266c3d4?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sknasib/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Sk Nasib Alam <small>(sknasib)</small></a> о <span class=\"review-date\">22 Листопада, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Field add Window, Header Button and Footer Button option not showing. When I set the screen Size 80% then those options are showing. Big issue.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Need WP Consent API to integrate with Complianz</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/carlodamo/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d5d458d14020e19716d2d66db583ac7c86e344286e392a1a2b55e952b026cb2b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d5d458d14020e19716d2d66db583ac7c86e344286e392a1a2b55e952b026cb2b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/carlodamo/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">carlodamo</a> о <span class=\"review-date\">21 Листопада, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Please, add WP Consent API to integrate with Complianz.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thanks</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Best Tool</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div clas