emplate=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/brakehuu/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4d95a7547a740c8865b4906686ded7cfee1d6805dfb298c07cae926ff8d2f6f9?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4d95a7547a740c8865b4906686ded7cfee1d6805dfb298c07cae926ff8d2f6f9?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/brakehuu/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">brakehuu</a> о <span class=\"review-date\">14 Грудня, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>LearnPress is hands-down one of the best WordPress LMS plugins I’ve ever used! From its robust functionality to the intuitive interface, it offers everything you need to create and manage an online education platform seamlessly.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>What I Loved:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Ease of Use:</strong> Setting up courses, quizzes, and lessons is straightforward, even for beginners.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Customization:</strong> The plugin provides a variety of settings and options to tailor the LMS to specific needs.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Scalability:</strong> It handles multiple courses and users without any hiccups, making it perfect for growing educational platforms.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Integration:</strong> The compatibility with payment gateways, themes, and add-ons is exceptional.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Support:</strong> The documentation is thorough, and the support team is responsive and helpful.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The code quality is outstanding, ensuring smooth performance and reliability. I’ve had zero issues with bugs or conflicts with other plugins. Highly recommend LearnPress to anyone building an online learning platform!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Same some time</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/artoftech/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8966d92d86b4adfc8571e1ae949016d7f6e804813ea78b3ba3a8d654a89c4986?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8966d92d86b4adfc8571e1ae949016d7f6e804813ea78b3ba3a8d654a89c4986?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/artoftech/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">John <small>(artoftech)</small></a> о <span class=\"review-date\">10 Грудня, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Less hassle out of the box. Excellent choice for an all-around simple to use LMS. Wish I\'d looked at it before all the others...</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Powerful plugin. Stop. Hardworking support. Stop. Free. Stop.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/desawebsup/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a2abb3a6ca3cee0dfc35b73fc6700dec42501af44a87cf3cdd1657f13e1fc4e8?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a2abb3a6ca3cee0dfc35b73fc6700dec42501af44a87cf3cdd1657f13e1fc4e8?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/desawebsup/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Desa_Web_Sup <small>(desawebsup)</small></a> о <span class=\"review-date\">12 Листопада, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Learnpress is a good plugin for managing and selling courses. Very good plugin, really. It has a multitude of well-thought-out functions, the management is intuitive, many add-ons and if you combine it with Woocommerce (instead of using its native checkount), sales improve a lot.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The support is very dedicated and willing to help.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All of this being FREE.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It is almost at the level of paid competitors.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Bad things:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Could be improved in terms of performance speed. Requires page load reduction work.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Low integration with subscription systems for the sale of courses. There are plugins that help, you can sell by subscription with LP, but plugin could increase communication between the plugins and improve automations. (PMPO is not a good partner to sell subscriptions and the other two \"big\" subscriptions plugins aren\'t be totally connected to LP).</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>The use of language files for translation could be improved.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>But in general it is a very efficient plugin for a learning website and with many constant improvements.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>And seriously, very good support.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excellence</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-fille