	<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">A Once-Reliable LMS Plugin Undermined by a Flawed 3.0 to 3.1.0 Updates.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sourabh29/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b15b84e4eb5c531b605708480fdf1563f7b858fb7d2e6ef09f6ea11341d56751?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b15b84e4eb5c531b605708480fdf1563f7b858fb7d2e6ef09f6ea11341d56751?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sourabh29/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">sourabh29</a> о <span class=\"review-date\">19 Грудня, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tutor LMS was once a cornerstone of efficiency and reliability, but the release of version 3.0 till 3.1.0 has been deeply disappointing. The update is riddled with critical bugs, severely disrupting its functionality and causing significant challenges.<br />With the new update even no course can be added nor the old ones can be edited.<br />What’s more disheartening is the lack of responsiveness from the support team despite repeated attempts to seek assistance.😞<br />Urgent action is required to resolve these issues or revert to a stable version, as the current state is untenable for professional use.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Beyond &quot;Extraordinary&quot;</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dofalex/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b1ac507bafa7fc5f8a551869197d03bc40c8e400c73adb8e5511c8c7f35d5775?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b1ac507bafa7fc5f8a551869197d03bc40c8e400c73adb8e5511c8c7f35d5775?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dofalex/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">dofalex</a> о <span class=\"review-date\">5 Грудня, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Great plugin, great tech support. It doesn\'t matter what kind of issue your website is dealing with, Tutor LMS staff always find the best solution for you in no time! I got the chance to work with developers <em>\"Nafiz &amp; Parag\"</em> and they were so <strong>HELPFUL.</strong> To me, they are over-skilled to resolve any issue on your website.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">very basic lms but claims most advanced</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"2 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"2\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/oumz99/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/06ea689056336cd9b8aae54102ec2d91872b23b908b8899b24c8337ded4c3483?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/06ea689056336cd9b8aae54102ec2d91872b23b908b8899b24c8337ded4c3483?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/oumz99/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">oumz99</a> о <span class=\"review-date\">4 Грудня, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is a very very basic LMS and does a good job. But promoting itself as advanced LMS is really not justified. It is just a course builder, good for building documents and free courses.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Top-Notch Support, Amazing Plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/leoceles1987/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c677b4ce19f93f9b9b1fa4b3df5852a77bfa375d4085c4951988de273ab6084c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c677b4ce19f93f9b9b1fa4b3df5852a77bfa375d4085c4951988de273ab6084c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/leoceles1987/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">leoceles1987</a> о <span class=\"review-date\">3 Грудня, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>After sales support is crucial in any purchase and Tutor Team always delivers. They have an amazing team. I can understand some users pointing out bugs--which also happens even to Apple among others! What separates Tutor from others is their patience in resolving issues as long as you are able to describe it to them.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I am. Thankful :) 5 star!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very best LMS plugin I have experienced out there!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/taqwamasjid/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/87460549d756517c6aec17c31441984a199a4724b03d03f2fbc54ac197848ba5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/87460549d756517c6aec17c31441984a199a4724b03d03f2fbc54ac197848ba5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/taqwamasjid/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">TJ <small>(taqwamasjid)</small></a> о <span class=\"review-date\">3 Грудня, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In my opinion one of the very best LMS plugins out there, for anyone seriously looking to create an LMS website. I have had great assistance and support from their team, it would be great to be able to have 24/7 support or even be able to speak to someone on the line but I really can\'t complain. I was initially disappointed when they removed the lifetime plan option, but I am glad they brought it back and I plan to invest in it at some point soon; I have used their services for a year now and it has been top-notch, upwards and onwards!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Tutor 3.0: Stop changing flows and usability and broke things!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"2 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"2\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/flaviusv/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e2312591195d98ce55c851e4d91deb89fd2d91b759466a05c5a69b95f3a8bebd?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e2312591195d98ce55c851e4d91deb89fd2d91b759466a05c5a69b95f3a8bebd?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/flaviusv/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">flaviusv</a> о <span class=\"review-date\">28 Листопада, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>That\'s a great initiative to upgrade Tutor from time to time, but IS NOT SO GREAT when you change the flow, the user interface, and especially the new upgrade BROKE down things that previously worked fine. There is a rule: don\'t touch things that work well! Now we have to do a lot of work with testing the new flow, new courses, new things… and I hate that! If I bought one thing, let that thing as I bought it, don\'t change anything because I bought it because I need it as it initially was! Hope this makes sense to you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">LMS Pro update without full validation and Certificate Builder not working</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 з 5 зірок\" data-title-template=\"%s з 5 зірок\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Від <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pirouzi/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/015501c45699f7ee095b4d6c9692557a3c5841674dc5acb4fdeb673e46705a4c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/015501c45699f7ee095b4d6c9692557a3c5841674dc5acb4fdeb673e46705a4c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pirouzi/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Peivand Pirouzi <small>(pirouzi)</small></a> о <span class=\"review-date\">24 Листопада, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I would like to extend my gratitude to Mr. Nafiz for his expertise in resolving the issue caused by the recent update of LMS Pro 3 installed on my site.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> I was unable to generate any certificates for two days due to the certificate builder not functioning. In light of this experience, I hope that future updates to LMS Pro will include standard quality control measures prior to implementation.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I spent approximately 12 hours over two nights troubleshooting the issue, searching online for possible solutions, and ultimately lost my customized certificates. I had to redo the certificate customization and manually assign the newly customized certificates to each course, which added an additional four hours of adjustments and testing on my part.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>While I truly appreciate the speed and value of the customer service provided, I believe that this situation could have been prevented with proper system validation prior to the update, similar to practices followed by o