on</a> page for more information.\";s:12:\"installation\";s:534:\"If the auto-update is not working, verify that you have a valid LearnDash LMS license via LEARNDASH LMS &gt; SETTINGS &gt; LMS LICENSE.\r\n\r\nAlternatively, you always have the option to update manually. Please note, a full backup of your site is always recommended prior to updating.\r\n\r\nDeactivate and delete your current version of the add-on.\r\nDownload the latest version of the add-on from our support site.\r\nUpload the zipped file via PLUGINS &gt; ADD NEW, or to wp-content/plugins.\r\nActivate the add-on plugin via the PLUGINS menu.\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:2006:\"<strong>1.1.3.1</strong><br/><ul>\n<li>Fix - Resolved a fatal error when rendering certificate download URLs.</li>\n</ul>\n<br/><strong>1.1.3</strong><br/><ul>\n<li>Fix - Resolved an issue where certificate image upload doesn&#039;t attach it to the post directly.</li>\n<li>Fix - Resolved conflict with LearnDash Integrity hotlinking prevention feature that disabled an image from being loaded in a certificate.</li>\n<li>Tweak - Added support for .PNG background images.</li>\n</ul>\n<br/><strong>1.1.3</strong><br/><ul>\n<li>Fix - Resolved an issue where certificate image upload doesn&#039;t attach it to the post directly.</li>\n<li>Fix - Resolved conflict with LearnDash Integrity hotlinking prevention feature that disabled an image from being loaded in a certificate.</li>\n<li>Tweak - Added support for .PNG background images.</li>\n</ul>\n<br/><strong>1.1.2</strong><br/><ul>\n<li>Tweak - Added the ability to filter the blocks that can be used within the certificate builder.</li>\n<li>Tweak - Added filters: <code>learndash_certificate_builder_allowed_blocks</code>, <code>learndash_certificate_builder_block_fallback</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n<br/><strong>1.1.1</strong><br/><ul>\n<li>Fix = Resolved missing blocks on widgets block editor page.</li>\n</ul>\n<br/><strong>1.1.0</strong><br/><ul>\n<li>Fix - Resolved fatal error related to non-prefixed Composer dependencies</li>\n<li>Tweak - Added actions: <code>learndash_certificate_builder_uninstall</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n<br/><strong>1.0.4</strong><br/><ul>\n<li>Fix - Show certificate background image when site is using self signed SSL certificate.</li>\n<li>Fix - Certificate displaying on multiple pages when using the columns block.</li>\n<li>Fix - Linebreaks breaking up words instead of moving to the next line.</li>\n<li>Fix - LearnDash Integrity prevent hotlinking feature causing background images to not display.</li>\n</ul>\n<br/><strong>1.0.3</strong><br/><ul>\n<li>Added support for WordPress 5.8</li>\n<li>Fixed font conflict with the Gutenberg plugin</li>\n</ul>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:53:\"Create certificates using the Gutenberg block editor.\";s:7:\"banners\";a:2:{s:3:\"low\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"high\";s:85:\"https://plugins.learndash.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/learndash-default_banner.jpg\";}s:11:\"screenshots\";a:1:{i:0;s:85:\"https://plugins.learndash.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/learndash-default_banner.jpg\";}s:5:\"icons\";a:1:{s:7:\"default\";s:76:\"https://plugins.learndash.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ld-plugin-image.jpg\";}s:6:\"author\";s:9:\"LearnDash\";s:10:\"author_uri\";s:26:\"https://www.learndash.com/\";s:11:\"requires_ld\";s:3:\"3.0\";s:10:\"plugin_uri\";s:48:\"https://learndash.com/add-on/certificate-builder\";s:4:\"tags\";s:52:\"certificates, course certificates, quiz certificates\";s:4:\"slug\";s:29:\"learndash-certificate-builder\";s:12:\"product_type\";s:8:\"standard\";}s:16:\"learndash-stripe\";a:20:{s:4:\"name\";s:20:\"Stripe for LearnDash\";s:10:\"project_id\";i:56;s:14:\"latest_version\";s:5:\"1.9.3\";s:12:\"download_url\";s:89:\"https://checkout.learndash.com/wp-json/learndash/v2/repo/plugin/learndash-stripe/download\";s:8:\"requires\";s:3:\"5.0\";s:6:\"tested\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"requires_php\";s:3:\"7.0\";s:12:\"last_updated\";s:19:\"2023-01-19 16:56:56\";s:8:\"sections\";a:3:{s:11:\"description\";s:592:\"Integrate LearnDash LMS with Stripe.\r\n\r\nLearnDash comes with the ability to accept payment for courses by leveraging PayPal. Using this add-on, you can quickly and easily accept payments using the Stripe payment gateway. Use it with PayPal, or just use Stripe - the choice is yours!\r\n<h4>Integration Features</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Accept payments using Stripe</li>\r\n 	<li>Automatic user creation and enrollment</li>\r\n 	<li>Compatible with built-in PayPal option</li>\r\n 	<li>Lightbox overlay</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSee the <a href=\"https://learndash.com/add-on/stripe/\">Add-on</a> page for more information.\";s:12:\"installation\";s:542:\"If the auto-update is not working, verify that you have a valid LearnDash LMS license via LEARNDASH LMS &gt; SETTINGS &gt; LMS LICENSE.\r\n\r\nAlternatively, you always have the option to update manually. Please note, a full backup of your site is always recommended prior to updating.\r\n\r\n 	Deactivate and delete your current version of the add-on.\r\n 	Download the latest version of the add-on from our support site.\r\n 	Upload the zipped file via PLUGINS &gt; ADD NEW, or to wp-content/plugins.\r\n 	Activate the add-on plugin via the PLUGINS menu.\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:611:\"<strong>1.9.3</strong><br/><ul>\n<li>Added coupon support</li>\n<li>Added support to the new LearnDash global default currency configuration</li>\n</ul>\n<br/><strong>1.9.2</strong><br/><ul>\n<li>Fixed PHP notice in legacy checkout</li>\n<li>Fixed empty amount in transaction record for recurring payments</li>\n<li>Fixed incorrect label on translations page</li>\n<li>Fixed Stripe payment button not honoring the &quot;active&quot; status for the gateway to be active or inactive</li>\n<li>Fixed LearnDash purchase emails not sending </li>\n<li>Fixed checkout not working for amounts under 10 in any currency</li>\n</ul>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:36:\"Integrate LearnDash LMS with Stripe.\";s:7:\"banners\";a:2:{s:3:\"low\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"high\";s:84:\"https://plugins.learndash.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/learndash-stripe_banner.jpg\";}s:11:\"screenshots\";a:1:{i:0;s:84:\"https://plugins.learndash.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/learndash-stripe_banner.jpg\";}s:5:\"icons\";a:1:{s:7:\"default\";s:85:\"https://plugins.learndash.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/learndash-stripe_256x256.jpg\";}s:6:\"author\";s:9:\"LearnDash\";s:10:\"author_uri\";s:26:\"https://www.learndash.com/\";s:11:\"requires_ld\";s:3:\"3.0\";s:10:\"plugin_uri\";s:36:\"https://learndash.com/add-on/stripe/\";s:4:\"tags\";s:36:\"integration, payment gateway, stripe\";s:4:\"slug\";s:16:\"learndash-stripe\";s:12:\"product_type\";s:8:\"standard\";}s:16:\"learndash-zapier\";a:20:{s:4:\"name\";s:20:\"Zapier for LearnDash\";s:10:\"project_id\";i:55;s:14:\"latest_version\";s:7:\"2.3.0.1\";s:12:\"download_url\";s:89:\"https://checkout.learndash.com/wp-json/learndash/v2/repo/plugin/learndash-zapier/download\";s:8:\"requires\";s:3:\"5.0\";s:6:\"tested\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"requires_php\";s:1:\"7\";s:12:\"last_updated\";s:19:\"2023-06-01 16:05:24\";s:8:\"sections\";a:3:{s:11:\"description\";s:691:\"Integrate LearnDash LMS with Zapier.\r\n\r\nZapier is a service that makes it easy for you to connect two applications without the need to know code, currently with a library of over 300 applications. Zapier calls these connections Zaps, and this integration lets you create Zaps that include LearnDash activities.\r\n<h4>Integration Features</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Perform actions in over 300 applications based on seven specific LearnDash activities</li>\r\n 	<li>Supports both global and specific LearnDash activity</li>\r\n 	<li>Easily connect LearnDash to the popular Zapier program without code</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSee the <a href=\"https://learndash.com/add-on/zapier/\">Add-on</a> page for more information.\";s:12:\"installation\";s:534:\"If the auto-update is not working, verify that you have a valid LearnDash LMS license via LEARNDASH LMS &gt; SETTINGS &gt; LMS LICENSE.\r\n\r\nAlternati